UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Feeling a little down?  Need some energy?  how about some hot fiery incendiary energy?$B$BTry the LAVA BLAST from Pyroco.  You\'ll fall in love with its sweet, refreshing taste and the raw power within.  Need a quick pick me up?  No problem! LAVA BLAST will rejuvenate you even at your most exhausted.' WHERE entry=3398; /* text: Feeling a little down?  Need some energy?  how about some hot fiery incendiary energy?$B$BTry the LAVA BLAST from Pyroco.  You\'ll fall in love with its sweet, refreshing taste and the raw power within.  Need a quick pick me up?  No problem! LAVA BLAST will rejuvenate you even at your most exhausted. */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Severly injured? we got you covered!  LAVA BLAST will give you that extra energy you need to find your way to safty!  Do you love fire?  Have you ever thought about how awsome it would be to drink liquid fire?  If so, you\'ll love new LAVA BLAST from Pyroco!  Taste the burning!$B$BRecent studies have hown that lava blast may not actually assist in healing wounds in anyway.  There is a possibilty that Lava Blast may actually cause you to bleed profusely from seemingly random orfices.' WHERE entry=3399; /* text: Severly injured? we got you covered!  LAVA BLAST will give you that extra energy you need to find your way to safty!  Do you love fire?  Have you ever thought about how awsome it would be to drink liquid fire?  If so, you\'ll love new LAVA BLAST from Pyroco!  Taste the burning!$B$BRecent studies have hown that lava blast may not actually assist in healing wounds in anyway.  There is a possibilty that Lava Blast may actually cause you to bleed profusely from seemingly random orfices. */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Warning Lava Blast is not for everyone, Pregnant Women, Children, and Women who might become pregnat or are nursing should consult their doctor before drinking Lava Burst.' WHERE entry=3400; /* text: Warning Lava Blast is not for everyone, Pregnant Women, Children, and Women who might become pregnat or are nursing should consult their doctor before drinking Lava Burst. */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Possible side affects may include,  Dry Mouth,  Upset Stomach, Dry Eyes, Indigestion, Back Pain, Bone and Joint Pain, Slight Disconfiguration, Internat Bleeding, Temporary Insanity, Lava Blast Addiction, Magic Addiction, Pyromania, Fear of Spiders, Lightning Eyes, Heart Palpitations, Fever, Spontaneous Child Birth, Lack of Sleep, Vulnerability to Cold Iron, Hysteria, Random Songs Popping Into Your Head, Asthma, Demonic Possession, Headaces, Footaches, The Inability to Use the Letter "R", and Death.' WHERE entry=3401; /* text: Possible side affects may include,  Dry Mouth,  Upset Stomach, Dry Eyes, Indigestion, Back Pain, Bone and Joint Pain, Slight Disconfiguration, Internat Bleeding, Temporary Insanity, Lava Blast Addiction, Magic Addiction, Pyromania, Fear of Spiders, Lightning Eyes, Heart Palpitations, Fever, Spontaneous Child Birth, Lack of Sleep, Vulnerability to Cold Iron, Hysteria, Random Songs Popping Into Your Head, Asthma, Demonic Possession, Headaces, Footaches, The Inability to Use the Letter "R", and Death. */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Caution drinking multiple Lava Blasts in rapid sucession can result in spontaneous combustion.$B$BTry new LAVA BLAST now!' WHERE entry=3402; /* text: Caution drinking multiple Lava Blasts in rapid sucession can result in spontaneous combustion.$B$BTry new LAVA BLAST now! */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Rule #4: Do not have someone who is polymorphed enter a portal. This has yet to not cause an explosion. This is also covered in "Polymorphic Rules & Regulations."
' WHERE entry=3451; /* text: Rule #4: Do not have someone who is polymorphed enter a portal. This has yet to not cause an explosion. This is also covered in "Polymorphic Rules & Regulations." */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Rule #5: Do not remove the liquid filter from a portal spell. Portals innately prevent large amounts of flowing water through them so that they can be cast underwater. To allow for water elementals to use a portal, this filter can be omitted when casting. Do not omit this when underwater! We feel obligated to mention Moderately Severe Claims Disaster Case 34-zz: "The Great Lakeshire Drought & The Great Ironforge Flood of 24 A.D."
' WHERE entry=3452; /* text: Rule #5: Do not remove the liquid filter from a portal spell. Portals innately prevent large amounts of flowing water through them so that they can be cast underwater. To allow for water elementals to use a portal, this filter can be omitted when casting. Do not omit this when underwater! We feel obligated to mention Moderately Severe Claims Disaster Case 34-zz: "The Great Lakeshire Drought & The Great Ironforge Flood of 24 A.D." */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Rule #5: Do not polymorph anything that is halfway through a portal - This has yet to not cause an explosion. This is also covered in "Thinking with Portals: A Memorandum on Proper Portal Usage."' WHERE entry=3459; /* text: Rule #5: Do not polymorph anything that is halfway through a portal - This has yet to not cause an explosion. This is also covered in "Thinking with Portals: A Memorandum on Proper Portal Usage." */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='<This flier was recently pasted here. Residue of glue on the stone shows that many fliers have previously occupied this location.>' WHERE entry=3477; /* text: <This flier was recently pasted here. Residue of glue on the stone shows that many fliers have previously occupied this location.> */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Hark!

Magic is not what you have been taught. Its dangers far exceed the greatest gifts it may bring! Question your Elders, that you may know the truth. Act now while there is time to save yourselves! Learn the ways of Nature and share in the balance of all things, ere your destructive ways upset it beyond repair.

<An unfamiliar seal decorates the bottom of the flier.>' WHERE entry=3478; /* text: Hark!

Magic is not what you have been taught. Its dangers far exceed the greatest gifts it may bring! Question your Elders, that you may know the truth. Act now while there is time to save yourselves! Learn the ways of Nature and share in the balance of all things, ere your destructive ways upset it beyond repair.

<An unfamiliar seal decorates the bottom of the flier.> */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Gunther Arcanus

Presumably killed during the events of the third war and lost to the Scourge.

Gunther was last in possession of my favorite pipe. Should his remains turn up, I would be most gracious for its return!' WHERE entry=3480; /* text: Gunther Arcanus

Presumably killed during the events of the third war and lost to the Scourge.

Gunther was last in possession of my favorite pipe. Should his remains turn up, I would be most gracious for its return! */
